						ἐν ἐξοχῆ.
					</marginalia_text>
				</position>
			</language>
			<language ident="LA">
				<position book_orientation="270" place="right_margin">
					<marginalia_text>
						Vtriusq[ue] triplex: et ter, quaterq[ue] sublimata. Quantas esse potest,
					</marginalia_text>
				</position>
				<position book_orientation="270" place="intext">
					<marginalia_text>
						a[e]thereo habitu.
					</marginalia_text>
				</position>
			</language>
			<translation>
				Actualization always at its peak, and daily refinement standing out.
				Three times of both; and thrice,  and four times elevated. As many times
				as can be done with a lofty habit.
			</translation>
		</marginalia>
		
